text: Great Central Location, home and lot! Take a look at this cute 2 bedroom craftsman home on a .95 flat sunny lot. This home has been tastefully updated with a newer kitchen and bathroom. Fresh paint on the inside makes it ready to move in! Newer furnace as well as a pellet stove in both the home and shop. Enjoy the back covered patio or stay out of the rain in the back sunroom. There is a spacious detached garage with room for 1-2 cars or shop space, plus shop space behind the and a one car carport. Also room on this lot to add a mega shop in the back NE corner! new 3 bedroom septic.Great option to expand or add an attached ADU. Sale includes both metal/glass carport in front and back gazebo.

Welcome to your new home in the heart of Bellingham! The nearby WWU makes this a tremendous opportunity. This move-in ready condo unit in the Puget neighborhood offers unparalleled convenience. Key features include its prime location; the second-floor unit just 500 feet from Whole Foods, Fred Meyer, public transit, Civic Field, Arne Hanna Aquatic Center, and trails. Inside, the unit boasts newer luxury vinyl plank flooring and all appliances, including a washer and dryer. This condo is not just a comfortable living space, but also a versatile investment opportunity. Whether you choose to make it your personal residence or a strategic investment, this charming condo is ready for you to make it your own.

Here we have a rare opportunity to own the ONLY vacant lot on Lake Whatcom. Boasting over 10, 000 sq/ft of flat, sunny land with 100 of lakefront, this is not one to miss! With city water & sewer already on site, you can begin enjoying your tranquil getaway on day one! This property has numerous sheds on site including one with power for convenient storing equipment or recreational gear. The large dock with covered boat lift makes summer lake days a blast! Moreover, the property's proximity to town offers the best of both worlds - the tranquility of lakeside living coupled with the convenience of urban amenities nearby. This blend of natural beauty and accessibility makes it an ideal location to fulfill the dream of building a custom home!

Welcome to this 5-acre lifestyle property offering endless possibilities! This charming 1910 two-story farmhouse features a cozy propane fireplace, mini-split heating & cooling, and natural light throughout. Perfect for equestrian enthusiasts, with a 3-stall horse barn, outdoor arena, all-weather lunging pad, and well-draining pastures. Aviation lovers will appreciate the private airplane hangar and access to Meadow Mist Airfield. The spacious shop w/ insulated room, automatic generator, and serene surroundings make it ideal for event hosting, hobby farming, flower farming, or creating your dream retreat. Imagine hosting weddings, retreats, or turning the land into a thriving dahlia farm. A rare find just minutes from Bellingham & Lynden!

Your wait is over! Beautifully updated 3 bed 2 bath home, fully insulated shop (26'x36'), w/10'x26' loft, lg flex space (possible ADU?), 12' rollup door, & garden shed. All located on an oversized, level, city serviced lot w/RV parking & hookups! Chefs kitchen w/expansive stone countertops, vaulted ceilings, stainless appliances, & a nice walk-in-pantry. Primary suite w/views of Mt Baker, huge walk-in closet, dual vanities, & slider to large covered patio/private fenced backyard boasting a fire pit & water feature. Near new: furnace, A/C, water heater, free standing stove, & ducting! Gen trans switch for outages. This home is perfect for get togethers, entertaining and enjoying our PNW summers. Bring your toys, hobbies, crafts & more!

Discover the charm of this 2+ bedroom Sunnyland bungalow, bursting with warmth and character! High ceilings, radiant heated kitchen floor, new soapstone countertops, new tile backsplash, a professional stove, and abundant cabinetry offer style and function, with bamboo and cork floors adding natural appeal. Modern updates include plumbing, electrical, windows, and a tankless water heater. The finished loft with a half bath and skylight makes an ideal flex space to match your lifestyle. Enjoy the lush yard with many edible and ornamental plants, plus a large back deck ready for your gas grill or firepitideal for summer evenings. Detached garage and walkable to Trader Joes, Avenue Bread, Kulshan Brewery, and morethis is a true urban oasis!

Rare opportunity to have a new home in the desirable Ridgemont neighborhood with Southside schools. This gorgeous home by Slusher Luxury Homes has an extensive list of upgrades that include a 8' island kitchen complete with Thermador commercial apps, quartz c/tops & huge pantry. The main floor of this contemporary designed home also has 9' ceilings on both floors, a 46 linear f/p, an open living & dining room concept, large study + separate den, custom mud room & is complete with engineered hardwood flooring. Upstairs enjoy a spacious primary bdrm & closet with 4 piece bath & huge flex space. This home is complete with a beautiful 22x28 covered patio with a huge panoramic sliding door, detailed T&G ceiling and built-in BBQ & 2 paddle fans!

Recently re-priced 2400+sqft garden home in quiet Bellingham neighborhood lives large on 1 level. Custom-built for comfort & convenience, inviting the outdoors in through south-facing windows, skylights and sliders. Private EZ care landscaped grounds border 12-acre greenspace. Chef's kitchen w/ Juparana Giavota granite island, canopy hood and extensive storage. Sunken living w/ vaulted ceilings & gas fireplace. Primary suite has walk-in shower, walk-through closet & private access to brand new hot tub. Cherry paneling in the French doored office + built-in cherry buffet in dining. Guest wing features bedroom, full bath and nook w/ built-in bunkbeds! Fresh exterior paint, true laundry room and cadillac AC all on a non-through street

Nestled in historic Edgemoor sits this charming Swiss Chalet-styled home. Perfectly situated in a cul-de-sac above a protected heron habitat, and a cleared scenic walking trail. Enjoy unobstructed views of South Hill, Bellingham Bay, the Cascade Mountains, Canadian Rockies and breathtaking sunsets. Inside you'll find two bedrooms with the flexibility to convert the family room into a third bedroom, a gorgeous sun room/dining area & a deck area to take in all this Beauty. Just a short stroll to ALL the amenities downtown Fairhaven has to offer. Enjoy easy access to the interurban trails, Taylor Boardwalk, Amtrak, and the Ferry terminal. Don't miss this rare opportunity to own a slice of Bellingham's lifestyle on this laid back street.

Looking for the Bellingham Unicorn? This 4+ bedroom home in town with a large lot, privacy and only 5 minutes to shops/dining is it! Enjoy this well-maintained home on a .23 acre professionally landscaped, fully fenced corner lot with a hot tub ready pergola and a 7x10 shed on concrete slab. Savor your morning coffee by the sunroom fireplace or on the 17x17 covered patio while you listen to the birds sing in the treetops. The main level has 2 bedrooms and a large living area that allows for a flexible configuration. The lower level has 2 bedrooms, full bath, add'l living space that can be an office, gym, or 5th bedroom as well as access to the yard and full 2 car garage. Dont miss the pet wash station and new AC unit.

This 3 bed, 2 bath home is situated in the back of the park on a desirable corner lot within a 55+ community, just minutes from I-5 and the amenities of Fairhaven. Featuring an attached 2 car garage and a fully fenced backyard, this home offers both convenience and privacy. Enjoy the outdoors year-round with a covered deck, & additional storage space provided by the shed. The interior is a spacious, open layout, with large closets. Monthly dues of $725 covers water, sewer, & cable TV. Residents of this community enjoy access to a well-appointed clubhouse that includes a gym, game tables, library, & more. Dont miss this opportunity to live in a peaceful, private home with easy access to shopping, banking and all that Fairhaven has to offer!

950+ sq ft. 2 bed, 1 bath stick build home, on a corner lot. Amazing location right across the street from the city park which is a block from downtown. Fenced area for the pet. Easy maintained yard. No water damage from last years epic flooding.

3 bed, 1 bath home tucked away on a dead end private cul de sac, backs to privacy with trees and greenbelt. 3 bed 1 bath home ready for you to move in and put your on design spin on it. Recently updated with double pane windows, mini split for heating and cooling purposes and a wood burning stove. Enjoy a short scenic drive to Mt Baker Ski resort. Just 35 minutes to Bellingham, minutes to the Canadian border, trails, parks and all things nature!

Welcome to Douglas Farm - a charming new community in Ferndale - close to Bellingham & the border! This beautiful Bedford plan w/high end features & smartly designed living spaces backs to the community park. The main floor features an inviting great room w/cozy FP & gourmet kitchen w/massive island, 5 burner gas cooktop, walk-in pantry & adjacent sunroom plus a powder room, pocket office & covered patio. Upstairs, you'll find a primary suite w/lavish bath, 2 secondary BRs, a spacious loft & utility rm. Extras include landscaping, irrigation, fencing, 9 ft ceilings, central heating/cooling, EV charging & more! If working w/a licensed broker, please register your broker on your 1st visit per our site reg policy. ASK ABOUT SPECIAL FINANCING!

Welcome to this beautifully updated 2-bedroom, 1-bath coastal gem that feels much larger than its square footage suggests. Filled with natural light and featuring a thoughtfully open layout, the home offers a modern kitchen and cozy living spaces. Just steps from the beach and walking path, enjoy a peekaboo view of the bay and the beauty of Birch Bays tide flats, perfect for beachcombing and sunset strolls. Situated in a charming community, this home is ideal as a serene primary residence or an excellent short-term rental opportunity. Embrace the best of Birch Bay living!

Accepting Back-ups. Presenting a completely renovated home located within Sunrise Community off of Alabama Hill. This sought-after neighborhood includes swimming pool, spa, dry sauna, tennis/pickleball court and fitness gym. HOA fee $96/month Upgrades include: luxury vinyl plank flooring, Energy Star Certified windows, French door leading to the back patio, front and interior doors, kitchen cabinets, quartz countertops, stainless steel sink, Whirlpool refrigerator and microwave, Bosch dishwasher, GE gas oven. Large 75 gallon water heater, central heating and air conditioner, bathroom vanities and fixtures, light fixtures throughout. Exterior and interior paint and gutters. New insulation in attic and under house. Interior is like new

Refined living. Nature at your door step. You'll be captivated by the walls of windows that fill the interior with natural light accentuating the beautiful finishes. Dedicated office/den with French doors. Sophisticated kitchen with a large island, is a culinary delight. Main primary suite provides a serene escape with a walk-in closet and a luxurious en-suite bathroom. Great room with a cozy gas fireplace. Marvel at the breathtaking backyard oasis - landscaped, fully-fenced with walkways, firepit, outbuilding, garden area + grassy lawn. 4th bedroom could be bonus room or art studio. 2-car garage with laundry sink + pull down ladder for storage. Nestled near the Galbraith Trails, this home perfectly blends convenience with tranquility.

Beautiful 3-bedroom, 2.5-bathroom with 2, 625 sqft of comfortable living space. Kitchen with granite countertops, stainless steel appliances, custom cabinets. Primary bedroom with en suite that includes radiant heating, a walk-in closet, vaulted ceiling, ceiling fan, and a cozy fireplace. Enjoy a versatile den/office, open floor plan, bamboo flooring, french doors, large separate entertainment room, and A/C. Yard fully fenced with composite deck to entertain your friends. This freshly painted one-story home was remodeled in 2012.

Rare find-One of a kind Contemporary stick build (container style home) on wooded rare 2+ acres inside the city limits. Everything on one level - 3 bedrooms, 3 baths, lots of upgrades throughout, to many to list. Modular design with abundance of windows overlooking park like setting. Large gourmet kitchen with Bosh and GE Monogram appliances, laminated floors, LED lighting throughout make it easy to maintain. Just a hop skip and a jump to Canadian border, shopping, parks, and schools. Large two car garage, gated courtyard, fenced in garden space with fruit trees. Stop by and see!

Incredible opportunity to buy a park model home at The Glen at Maple Falls! Health issues force sale. This '94 Wedgewood Park park model is in good shape. When you step in the back door, you have a private sunken primary bedroom. Above the bedroom is a loft for 2 to 4 people. Then, there is another door that has 2 private bunks! Full size bath, and plenty of room in the kitchen, with a dining area. Large living room area. This also has a covered deck for barbequing. Firepit out front ready for entertaining! Also has storage shed. Everything there stays! The Glen has 2 pools (1 open year-round) hot tub, sauna, tennis & pickleball courts, river access, 24/7 security, laundry & shower facilities, trails, and so much more. Minutes to Mt. Baker!

Great opportunity to stop paying someone else's mortgage and get started in home ownership. Prime property to use as a stepping stone to your ultimate home. THEN/OR it becomes a sound addition to your real estate income portfolio. Home , septic , landscape and everything here is only 5 years old so many more years of worry free, hassle free living or rent collection with low low expenses. Solid easy care home and property in close proximity to some of the counties largest employers and minutes to Birch Bay beaches and recreational activities that insure long-term value and consistent returns. 3 beds, 2 baths , 1080 sf - this is a sweet little place with easy I-5 access on one side and tons of fun on the other.

This lovingly maintained Mallard trailer sits on a corner lot in division two. Trees give some privacy from the road, and a shed sits on the property for additional or larger storage. With two sleeping places, and a cozy living room, there is lots of space to relax and enjoy the comforts of this home away from home. The Glen is zoned recreational for 120 days of use out of the year and has all the amenities you could want, including 2 pools, hot tub, tennis court, library, laundry mat, 2 clubhouse, 24 hr security, gated entry, & play areas.

Stunning, one-of-a-kind, shy 7-acre property with a large covered deck that overlooks a private pond & a panorama mountain view. The beautiful log cabin features two bedrooms plus a loft, gorgeous vaulted ceilings, a 2nd deck off the primary bedroom, an updated kitchen and spacious bath, new light fixtures, a new range in '23, & tons of sun pouring in the new Anderson windows. The property features fruit trees, blueberries, currants, a serene willow tree grove, a mature treeline of evergreens for privacy on three sides, & an intimate trail from the southwest end of the circular driveway that leads you through the trees to a workshop, shed, & carport that are on a separate power meter. Only 10 minutes to Lynden & 15-20 minutes to Bellingham.

Discover this beautifully updated 4-bedroom, 2.25-bath Ferndale gem! Set on a spacious 9, 000+ sq. ft. lot in a scenic neighborhood, this 1, 872 sq. ft. two-level home blends modern finishes with cozy charm. Enjoy a kitchen with new appliances and quartz countertops, relax in the inviting living spaces, and appreciate the energy efficiency of electric furnace and heat pump for heating and cooling and a gas tankless water heater. Outdoors, a large backyard offers ample space for gardening, gatherings, and play, while a welcoming front porch and back deck invite year-round enjoyment. Complete with an attached garage, driveway, and extra parking, this home is perfect for Northwest living!

Meticulously maintained 3 yr new single level rambler on large professionally landscaped lot 15 min from DT B'ham. Escape to your private oasis nestled up to a protected wooded greenbelt. Custom steel raised planter boxes and outdoor firepit w/berries, fruit trees, sauna, gas plumbed grill, covered patio space and sprinkler system allow you to sit back, relax, and enjoy your surroundings. Approach your rocking chair front porch and enter into open oversized spaces, SS appliances, pendant lighting, custom tiled primary bath w/Todo toilet, 3 large bedrooms and dedicated office space. Better than new w/each detail thought out making this property truly move in ready.

Welcome to your charming new home in the desirable Birchwood neighborhood! This adorable 2-bedroom move-in ready gem offers cozy comfort and character, featuring beautiful hardwood floors and bright, sunny spaces throughout. Enjoy the large, fully fenced yardperfect for pets, gardening, or gatherings. The home sits on a spacious, sun-drenched lot with mature landscaping, creating a private outdoor retreat. Conveniently located close to amenities, youll have shops, dining, and parks just moments away. Enjoy a short walk to Locust Beach or Little Squalicum Beach. Dont miss this perfect blend of charm and convenience!

text: Airy contemporary home with views and access to the gorgeous falls of Austin Creek, right outside your door. The main floor master suite is bright and spacious and the living room is HUGE! The layout boasts a modern kitchen that overlooks the living room area. Upstairs are two generous bedrooms and a bonus room that could be easily converted to a 4th bedroom. Enjoy access to all Sudden Valley amenities: Marina, Beaches, Parks, Clubhouse, Fitness Center, Pools & more!

This home is located in Fairhaven's Parkway Village 55 and better active community. If you have been looking for a community to connect w/ and experience all that South Bellingham has to offer, this is it! Come look at this 1498 sqft, 2 bdrm + a den and a sunroom, 2 bathroom single-level home with an attached carport and storage area. The kitchen is light and bright with a skylight, updated kitchen cabinets and a huge pantry. The interior living areas have been freshly painted and carpets are cleaned. Enjoy the fully fenced-in backyard with a patio, apple tree, grape vines, and a mature landscape. This home is move-in ready for you; don't miss out on the opportunity to call this home!

This charming Lakeridge condo overlooks Sudden Valley's natural beauty in desirable Gate 2. Spacious & sun-filled home offers vaulted living room ceilings & privacy throughout. It has 2 sizeable bedrooms + office/bonus room that counts as a 3rd room & ample storage. Featuring both front & back decks, a sunny back deck where you can enjoy mountain & golf course views plus glimpses of Lake Whatcom & a private front porch that can be enjoyed as a shady oasis for peace & quiet. Friendly Lakeridge community fees cover a private pool, pickleball/tennis court & water/sewer. Access to scenic Lake Louise Trail just out your door & many beaches, trails & parks to explore throughout Sudden Valley. Great home or investment property, not at rental cap!

Embrace the potential of this estate property nestled by the tranquil Nooksack River. Spanning 2.25 acres of park-like grounds adorned with a serene pond and majestic cedar and fir trees, this home features a metal roof, inviting skylights, and the promise of a stunning fireplace as its centerpiece. Imagine the allure of leisurely evenings on the porch, accompanied by the soothing sounds of the river and local wildlife. Originally envisioned as a charming bed and breakfast, this property invites you to revive that dream or transform it into your ideal retreat. Conveniently located close to the Mount Baker Recreation area, where on can indulge in hiking, winter sports, fishing, and simply basking in nature's embrace.

Spectacular small acreage estate 2 story home offering 4 bedrooms, 2 living rooms, spacious kitchen with dining nook, formal dining room, and upstairs spacious primary with ensuite. Delightful south facing scenic picture windowed den/office/artist studio, 3 car attached garage, on landscaped 2+ acre level parcel is perfect for multiple residents. Needs a little TLC/updating. Conveniently located at end of no outlet pave street populated by small acreage trade up/luxury homes only minutes from downtown Blaine.

This delightful home, with its timeless charm and solid structure, offers an incredible opportunity for investment and customization. The standout feature of this property is its sprawling private yard, perfect for outdoor entertaining, gardening, or simply enjoying your own slice of serenity. Imagine summer barbecues, gatherings, or peaceful evenings in this beautiful, expansive space. Located in the vibrant, welcoming community of Ferndale, you have all the local amenities, parks, trails and shops near by, as well as 4 min I-5 access! With its friendly neighborhood and excellent schools, its potential for updates and the exceptional value of its large yard, this home is a true gem. Act quicklyproperties like this are hard to find!

Welcome to this beautiful 3 bed, 3 bath picture-perfect home, where comfort meets convenience in the desirable Whiskey Creek neighborhood. Built in 2014 and thoughtfully designed, the home features high ceilings, a beautiful kitchen with granite countertops, SS appliances, and hardwood flooring throughout. French doors open to a private, fully-fenced yardperfect for relaxation, gatherings, & your furry friends. The large primary bedroom boasts vaulted ceilings a walk-in closet and en suite bath. Located just off Portal Way, youre only 2 minutes from cruising on I-5 and 5 minutes from downtown Ferndale, with everything you need close by! This home is the ideal blend of privacy and proximity. Come explore your next chapter here!

Better than new stunning sun-drenched modern farmhouse on 5+ acres. Radiating PNW charm, the curb appeal sets the stage + every thoughtfully executed detail is spot on. Lives like a single level home (with only a bonus space above the 3 car garage), you'll love the ceiling height, open concept floor plan and the custom high end finishes. The primary suite is privately located away from the other 2 bedrooms and boasts a luxurious ensuite with under mount soaker tub & tiled shower. Energy efficient mini splits for heating/cooling, solar panels, LVP flooring, hand blown glass lights made from molds from the 1800s, covered back patio & delightful English garden vibe in the backyard. Bonus: RV pad with 50 amp power, water & sewer dump.

Charming 4-bedroom, 2-bath home with 1, 839 sq. ft. of living space on a quiet street, close to schools and a neighborhood park. This home features a cozy living room with a gas fireplace, air conditioning for year-round comfort, and a large front porch. The backyard includes a patio and a convenient shed for extra storage. An attached 2-car garage with alley access completes the package.

Welcome Home to your Bright, Top Floor Lynden Condo. Set in a Peaceful and Social 55+ Community, this Spacious 2013 built Home offers tall ceilings, a cozy Fireplace, and tons of Natural light, Primary bath with walk-in shower. Upgrades include Primary bedroom ceiling fan, smart control thermostat for HVAC; Kitchen under cabinet LED lighting and upgraded soft close drawers. Your unit enjoys its own, large/deep garage with included storage racks and floor matting. The Building shares several common areas for neighbor or gatherings, both indoor and outjoin in the Friday Happy Hour! This Gorgeous 4 bedroom 3 bathroom contemporary home is just what you have been looking for. Located in a very desirable Sudden Valley Community. Just the Place to call Home.

Nearly 5 acres of gently sloping land, 3 bedroom house, fruit orchard, wooded area, and a massive 2, 160 square foot shop, waiting for that special buyer who runs a home business, and/or needs to store your big toys! You must see inside this colossal shop to appreciate all the possibilities with gas heat and 220 electricity. SW facing property receives tons of sunlight. Main floor of the house has 2 bedroom, 1 bath, fireplace, with wood burning insert, sunroom, laundry room, and enormous west facing deck. Oak floors, granite kitchen countertops, and marble shower/bath, french doors and a charming window seat. Mostly finished basement: possible mother-in-law, with separate entrance, 3/4 bath, and additional rooms! Also attached garage.

One of a kind single level penthouse with bay, island, city, and epic sunset views in a coveted location at iconic Taylor Dock in Fairhaven! This stunning NEW residence represents a highly sought after boutique building, rarely available! Timeless sophistication with captivating design elements & top of the line finishes throughout. Enjoy walls of glass, soaring ceilings, and folding glass doors opening to a large, covered sundeck. Other features include 2 bedrooms, 2 baths, office, chef's kitchen, air conditioning, and a private 2 car garage. The feel of a single family home with the lock and leave lifestyle of a condo. Enjoy daily walks on the dock and Fairhaven's vibrant village with restaurants, stores, parks, all only steps away!

Rare offering on the south side - stunning luxury contemporary home situated on a 60 waterfront lot with no bank. Showcasing panoramic vistas of Mt. Baker, the San Juan Islands, and the Marina Breakwater. All year-round living, open, and light-filled living spaces that extend to the outdoors with expansive decks on both exposures. Architect-designed home featuring 3 beds, a main level den/office, and 3 baths. Private courtyard, a double car garage, and marina access right around the corner. Experience waterfront living in beautiful Point Roberts, less than 30 minutes from Vancouver, BC.

Come visit this home located in Baker Ridge, a gated community. It is front row facing east w/unobstructed views of Mt. Baker & the Twin Sisters. The home features a gourmet kitchen w/ample cabinets & counter space. Main floor features elegant primary suite, living & dining & family room. There are built in cabinets throughout & lots of storage. The main floor also features bedroom plus bath, powder room & spacious laundry room. Attached 3 car garage w/no threshold.Upper level has 2 bedrooms w/access to their own baths, great room w/kitchen & unfinished bonus room w/access to the garage. Multiple patios to enjoy the outside. Includes a 1418 sq. ft. 2X6 stick framed shop with loft. Community features a pickleball/basketball court plus more.

Live full-time or vacation just minutes from the beach in the picturesque beachfront community of Birch Bay, Washington. This affordable home boasts an excellent floor plan with a kitchen, open living room, and one bathroom, alongside two bedrooms for comfort and convenience. Enjoy ample parking with two assigned spaces and plenty of guest parking available. Immerse yourself in the vibrant coastal lifestyle of Birch Bay, offering beach walks, clamming, crabbing, waterslides, restaurants, and shops. Plus, indoor cats and friendly dogs welcome, every member of your clan can enjoy the coastal paradise of Birch Bay.

Welcome to Harborside Estates, where this charming home combines fantastic curb appeal with a prime location just minutes from Blaines vibrant downtown and local schools. Step inside to find a beautifully updated 3-bedroom, 2.5-bath retreat with an office. Featuring 9' ceilings, a modern kitchen with sleek grey cabinets, quartz countertops, air conditioning, and stainless steel appliances...this home is turnkey and move in ready. The primary suite offers a relaxing space with vaulted ceilings, a private balcony, and serene Birch Bay water views. Outside, enjoy a fully fenced backyard just steps from Montfort Park and easy beach access. Plus, a spacious 3-car garage awaits your vehicles and storage needs.

One of Bellingham's earlier homes in a well established and highly sought after neighborhood. Located in the Cornwall Park neighborhood it is an easy walk to both Cornwall and Broadway Parks. Off street parking in front and alley access with garage in the back. Nice little deck and fenced yard area. One level 1640 sf home with hardwood floors, 2 bedrooms and a fantastic 560 sf basement area. One walk thru and the possibilities jump out, so much to appreciate here. This 1924 beauty deserves a little TLC. Perfectly fine as is but is ready for some deferred maintenance and is priced accordingly.

text: Nestled on a sprawling half acre lot, you won't find another one like this fully remodeled mid-century Craftsmen. Wonderfully maintained and much-loved brick rambler located in the desirable Montfort Park neighborhood, offering serene views of Drayton Harbor. First time on the market! Parklike 4.9-acre property features a 5-bedroom, 2.25-bath tri-level home and a 30x96 shop. Meticulously taken care of with tasteful updates make this property a true gem! This updated rambler with a shop in a quiet mid-county neighborhood is the perfect place to call home! Fresh updates from floor to ceiling make this home turn-key! You'll love the new LVP flooring and white trim, updated bathroom, newer paint inside and out, and modern light fixtures.
